To list or see all users 

$ cat /etc/passwd

For bash users

$ compgen -u

For detailed view

$ grep "username" /etc/bash

To add new user in system

$ sudo adduser "userS"

Set password for new user

$ sudo passwd "user"

To confirm the user was added successfully

$ id "user"

To create user with Home Directory

$ usermod -m "user"

Remove a user (keep files):

$ sudo userdel username

Remove a user and their files:

$ sudo userdel -r username

Verify the Deletion

$ id username

